Context: The Personal Support Worker (PSW) program is offered online at George Brown College. The program is overseen by Christine Chan, the Program-Coordinator, who can be contacted at nursing@georgebrown.ca. Interested individuals can sign up to receive updates about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours by clicking "Sign Up Now". The college can be reached at 416-415-2000 or TTY: 1-877-515-5559. For general inquiries, individuals can email ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The information contained on the website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Prospective students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
